-- Israel
announced they're expanding the
settlements.

26:35.427 --> 26:40.833 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
We know the attitude about
Israel of the incoming
president-elect, Mr. Netanyahu.

26:40.866 --> 26:46.438 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
So, my question is, were you as
secretary
of state shouting into the wind?

26:46.472 --> 26:49.107 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
JOHN KERRY: No, I don't believe
so.

26:49.141 --> 26:51.143 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
I don't believe so at all.

26:51.176 --> 26:56.114 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Every administration through our
history has
said that the settlements are an
obstacle

26:56.148 --> 26:59.718 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
to peace and they do not have
legal validity.

26:59.751 --> 27:06.525 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
We didn't break new ground with
that, except
that we reiterated and
reaffirmed that we

27:06.558 --> 27:16.335 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
are not going to sit by idly and
watch a sort
of extreme element within the
current government

27:16.368 --> 27:25.777 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
move in a direction that we
believe is dangerous
for Israel, reduces the
possibility of peace,

27:25.811 --> 27:32.784 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
prolongs the potential of
conflict, and is
completely contrary to American
values and

27:32.818 --> 27:38.190 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
interests, which have been
expressed by Republican
and Democrat administrations
alike throughout

27:38.223 --> 27:39.191 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
history.

27:39.224 --> 27:41.693 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: Final question.

27:41.727 --> 27:46.532 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
You're seen as the most
shoulder-to-the-wheel
secretary of state we have had
in a long time.

27:46.565 --> 27:51.403 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
You have been to every --
virtually every
global -- or you have been
dealing with virtually

27:51.436 --> 27:56.008 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
every global trouble spot around
the world.

27:56.041 --> 27:59.044 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
You have given this job long
hours.

27:59.077 --> 28:02.414 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
You have traveled nonstop.

28:02.447 --> 28:03.916 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
What are you the most proud of?

28:03.949 --> 28:07.152 align:left position:12.5%,start line:80% size:87.5%
What is your greatest
disappointment as you
walk away?

28:07.185 --> 28:14.560 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JOHN KERRY: Well, you know, I'm
going to duck
you slightly here, in the sense
that I honestly

28:14.593 --> 28:16.261 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
don't dwell on the
disappointments.

28:16.295 --> 28:17.563 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
There are some.

28:17.596 --> 28:20.532 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
And we have talked about a few
of the things
that are undone.

28:20.566 --> 28:23.936 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
But I am very proud of the
department.

28:23.969 --> 28:30.976 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
I think we are more engaged in
more places
in the world, simultaneously
dealing with

28:31.009 --> 28:37.115 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
more crises, and with greater
effect in those
more places in the world, than
at any time

28:37.149 --> 28:38.517 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
