28:38.550 --> 28:42.487 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
I think the world is safer
without Iran with
a nuclear weapon.

28:42.521 --> 28:48.193 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
The world has got the potential
to be safer
if we fully implement the Paris
agreement.

28:48.226 --> 28:55.300 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
So, yes, I think, all in all,
the Obama administration
and what President Obama has
focused on has

28:55.334 --> 29:04.443 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
lived up to our need to protect
American interests,
to live our values and assert
our values,

29:04.476 --> 29:07.846 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
and to stand up for future
generations.

29:07.879 --> 29:13.085 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: Secretary of
State John Kerry,
thank you very much.

29:13.118 --> 29:20.993 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
JOHN KERRY: Thank you.

29:21.026 --> 29:27.432 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: And that brings
us to the analysis
of Shields and Brooks.

29:27.466 --> 29:31.236 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
