Brooks.

29:31.269 --> 29:32.237 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
Happy new year, gentlemen.

29:32.270 --> 29:33.238 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
MARK SHIELDS: Happy new year,
