29:35.107 --> 29:38.910 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
So, let's start by talking about
this intelligence
report.

29:38.944 --> 29:41.847 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
Mark, the entire intelligence
community is
behind it.

29:41.880 --> 29:47.185 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
They're saying without a shadow
of a doubt,
in so many words, they are
confident the Russians

29:47.219 --> 29:51.590 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
